veral 40+ SB's who happened to be pasing by on their way out into the frontier as I engaged a Frosty Colt.  BSII, TC, and then a string of 5 Evades and 5 Hamstrings.  Let me say, that was awesome, taking down a yellow con mob without taking anydamage at all from it.  I was 24 at the time.  Of course, the overconfidence got me killed as I got agroed by a Flurry a few minutes later, and instead of running thought&quot;I can take him&quot;, and promprtly got my A$$ handed to me by that DDing critter....  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
